Name: Gnomelings: Migration
About the game: In the land of Ventocia, the Gnomelings are on the move, but danger awaits them at every turn! Lava pits, death-traps, abyss-falls, and flying spears all stand between the Gnomelings and their new homeland. It's up to you and your VR controllers to make sure they arrive safely at their destination. Teach your Gnomelings to parachute, direct traffic, and generally help them avoid certain death. Use your hands for dozens of levels of crowd controlling puzzle action!
